{
  "id": "019d286a-f2d8-78b2-92cd-67fbee02e39f",
  "content": "### Task 2: CLI Scaffolding — WorkspaceCommands Enum\n\n\n```rust\n    /// Workspace management for multi-repo projects\n    Workspace {\n        #[command(subcommand)]\n        command: WorkspaceCommands,\n    },\n```\n\nAdd the dispatch arm in `main()`:\n\n```rust\n    Commands::Workspace { command } => cmd_workspace(command).await?,\n```\n\nAdd the stub handler:\n\n```rust\nasync fn cmd_workspace(command: WorkspaceCommands) -> Result<()> {\n    match command {\n        WorkspaceCommands::Create { name, repos, template, locals } => {\n            println!(\"workspace create: {} (repos: {:?})\", name, repos);\n            todo!(\"workspace create\")\n        }\n        WorkspaceCommands::Init => {\n            println!(\"workspace init\");\n            todo!(\"workspace init\")\n        }\n        WorkspaceCommands::Status => {\n            println!(\"workspace status\");\n            todo!(\"workspace status\")\n        }\n        WorkspaceCommands::Add { url, name, namespace, local } => {\n            println!(\"workspace add: {}\", url);\n            todo!(\"workspace add\")\n        }\n        WorkspaceCommands::Remove { name, purge } => {\n            println!(\"workspace remove: {}\", name);\n            todo!(\"workspace remove\")\n        }\n        WorkspaceCommands::Ingest { repo, fresh } => {\n            println!(\"workspace ingest\");\n            todo!(\"workspace ingest\")\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Verify it compiles and --help works**\n\nRun: `cargo build -p corvia-cli`\nExpected: compiles cleanly.\n\nRun: `cargo run -p corvia-cli -- workspace --help`\nExpected: shows workspace subcommands (create, init, status, add, remove, ingest).\n\nRun: `cargo run -p corvia-cli -- workspace create --help`\nExpected: shows create flags (name, --repo, --template, --local).\n\n**Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add crates/corvia-cli/src/main.rs\ngit commit -m \"feat(m2.1): scaffold corvia workspace CLI subcommand group\"\n```\n\n---\n",
